---
// No props needed
---
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
  <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
      <svg class="h-6 w-6 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
      </svg>
      Red Flag Guidance (Urgent Care)
    </h3>
    <p class="text-gray-800 mb-4 font-medium">Seek urgent local help or emergency services if there is:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
      <li>Risk of harm to self or others</li>
      <li>Abuse or neglect concerns</li>
      <li>Medical emergency</li>
      <li>Severe regression (loss of skills)</li>
      <li>Seizures or neurological concerns</li>
      <li>Suicidal statements</li>
      <li>Severe aggression causing immediate danger</li>
      <li>Sudden major behavioral change</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-brand-trust p-6 rounded-r-lg">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3">When to Seek Local Regulated Care</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-800 mb-4">You should seek out a local professional in your region for the following:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
      <li><strong>Diagnosis:</strong> Local Pediatrician or Developmental Pediatrician</li>
      <li><strong>Formal Assessment:</strong> Registered Psychologist</li>
      <li><strong>Medication:</strong> Psychiatrist or Pediatrician</li>
      <li><strong>Direct Therapy:</strong> Speech Therapist, Occupational Therapist</li>
      <li><strong>School System Intervention:</strong> School Psychologist or Special Needs Educator (SNE)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
